<headline>Special Weather Statement issued February 07 at 5:13AM EST  by NWS Grand Rapids</headline>
<description>...Locally Slick Travel Possible Early This Morning...
A thin layer of ice may develop on roads and sidewalks as an area of
freezing drizzle and light snow tracks southward through the region
early this morning. Be alert for possible slippery conditions through
the morning commute. Allow extra time to reach your destination.</description>
